  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Make a <strong>melee spell attack</strong> against a creature you can reach. On a miss, the spell ends. On a hit, the target takes <strong>8d6 cold damage</strong> and is affected by the spell.</p><p>While affected by this spell, a creature's speed is halved from its painful shivering. At the end of each of its turns, it takes <strong>2d6 cold damage</strong> and can make a <strong>Constitution saving throw</strong>, ending the spell on a success.</p><p>A creature immune to cold damage is immune to this spell.</p><p><strong><em>At Higher Levels:</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 5th level or higher, the initial damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 4th.</p>",
